OL,7,FA paramedic has told a trial that a
OL,8,Fpensioner allegedly unlawfully killed
OL,9,Fby her husband and son had severe open
OL,10,Fpressure sores which exposed her bones.
OL,12,FTwo men, Robert Morgan, 61 and David
OL,13,FHolyoak, 52, are on trial at Carlisle
OL,14,FCrown Court for the alleged
OL,15,Fmanslaughter of their respective wife
OL,16,Fand mum, Dorothy Morgan, by gross
OL,17,Fnegligence.
