OL,7,FGiving evidence on Thursday 25
OL,8,FJanuary, paramedic Rebecca Hodgson
OL,9,Fsaid she arrived at the trio's Calder
OL,10,FAvenue home in Whitehaven and found
OL,11,FMrs Morgan lying on her back on the
OL,12,Fliving room floor.
OL,14,FMorgan ` who had told the call
OL,15,Foperator he had just completed a 12-
OL,16,Fhour night shift ` was said to have
OL,17,Fstated that he "thought she was OK",
OL,18,Fand that he wasn't around very often
OL,19,Fas he worked in Barrow.
