OL,7,FMiss Hodgson was told Mrs Morgan had
OL,8,Fnot seen a doctor for some time. She
OL,9,Fwas conscious but unresponsive and
OL,10,F"very lethargic", said the medic. She
OL,11,Fdid, however, respond to pain as a
OL,12,Fcannula was inserted.
OL,14,FOxygen saturation levels were low,
OL,15,Fblood pressure readings were
OL,16,F"extremely low" and Mrs Morgan's heart
OL,17,Frate was slightly elevated. However,
OL,18,Freadings improved soon after after
OL,19,Ftreatment and physical therapy was
OL,20,Fadministered.
