OL,7,FIt was when Mrs Morgan was physically
OL,8,Fmoved that Miss Hodgson noted multiple
OL,9,Fpressure sores which, the court heard,
OL,10,Fwere graded "severe". "Very deep,"
OL,11,Fsaid the paramedic of those sores. "I
OL,12,Fcould see her bone on either side of
OL,13,Fthe upper legs."
OL,15,FMrs Morgan, acutely unwell, was taken
OL,16,Fto the West Cumberland Hospital in
OL,17,FWhitehaven where she was found to be
OL,18,Fclinically dehydrated and severely
OL,19,Fmalnourished.
