OL,7,FShe died 10 days later, on 4 February
OL,8,F2021.
OL,10,FEarlier in the day, jurors heard two
OL,11,Fphones made by the defendant Morgan on
OL,12,Fthe morning of 25 January 2021.
OL,14,F"I've got a problem with the wife," he
OL,15,Ffirst told a Cumbria Health on Call
OL,16,Fhandler. "She has literally tried to
OL,17,Fstarve herself to death over the last
OL,18,Fcouple of months. She has not allowed
OL,19,Fme to get in touch with any health
OL,20,Fprofessionals."
