OL,7,FHe added: "She looks like something
OL,8,Ffrom a death camp. She can't go on
OL,9,Flike this."
OL,11,FThat comment was repeated when Morgan
OL,12,Fdialled 999 and spoke to an operator
OL,13,Fseveral minutes later.
OL,15,F"The wife has been refusing to get any
OL,16,Fkind of medical help for months," he
OL,17,Fsaid. "She stopped eating. She stopped
OL,18,Fdrinking. She can barely sit up now."
