OL,7,F"I am not supporting behaviour like
OL,8,Fthis any more," he added. "It has gone
OL,9,Ftoo far."
OL,11,FIt is alleged by the prosecution that
OL,12,FMorgan and Holyoak, both of Calder
OL,13,FAvenue, Whitehaven, "stood by,
OL,14,Fallowed" and effectively "watched" as
OL,15,Ftheir wife and mother was "left to die
OL,16,Fin her own filth".
OL,18,FIt is further alleged that the pair
OL,19,F"completely failed to properly take
OL,20,Fcare of her, or at the very least get
OL,21,Fher some help".
