OL,7,FJurors have heard that, when
OL,8,Finterviewed by police, the two men
OL,9,Finsisted that they were following Mrs
OL,10,FMorgan's orders that no help be sought
OL,11,Fand that they were simply acting out
OL,12,Fher final wishes.
OL,14,FThe trial, which is expected to last
OL,15,Faround a fortnight, continues.
